This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the baidu organization:
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-21B-A3B-PT tokenizer.json
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-21B-A3B-Thinking tokenizer.json

The bundled `ernie-4.5` family covers the following official baidu models:
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-0.3B-PT
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-0.3B-Base-PT
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-21B-A3B-PT
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-21B-A3B-Base-PT
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-300B-A47B-PT
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-300B-A47B-Base-PT

The bundled `ernie-4.5-thinking` family covers the following official baidu model:
- baidu/ERNIE-4.5-21B-A3B-Thinking

